<placeName cert="high">Hermoupolis Magna</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Γερμανὸς Ἀπολλωνίωι τῶι 

    <lb n="2"/>τιμιωτάτωι χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>ἔπεμψά σοι διὰ Ἀπολλωνίου τοῦ 

    <lb n="4"/><choice><corr>μικροῦ</corr><sic>μεικρου</sic></choice> ἀργυρίου δραχμὰς εἴκοσι <num value="20"/> 

    <lb n="5"/>μεθ᾽ ἃς ἔδωκά σοι ἐν Λύκων πόλει 

    <lb n="6"/>δραχμὰς ἑκατόν <num value="100"/>. καλῶς οὖν ποι-

    <lb n="7"/>ήσεις, ἄδελφε, πέμψας μοι δι᾽ αὐ-

    <lb n="8"/>τοῦ ἢ δι᾽ οὗ ἐὰν θέλῃς ακουχους 

    <lb n="9"/>δέκα πέντε <num value="15"/>. καὶ σὲ δὲ προτρέ-

    <lb n="10"/>πομαι ἐπιτρέπειν μοι περὶ ὧν 

    <lb n="11"/>βούλει <choice><corr>ὡς</corr><sic>ος</sic></choice> ἥδιστα ποιήσοντι. 

    <lb n="12"/><handShift new="m2"/> ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι, 

    <lb n="13"/>τιμιώτατέ μοι ἄδελφε. 

    <lb n="14"/><handShift new="m3"/> ἔρρωσο. 

    <lb n="15"/><handShift new="m4"/> Ἁθὺρ <num value="12">ιβ</num> 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="16"/><handShift new="m5"/> Ἁπολλωνίωι στρατηγ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῶι</supplied> <expan>Ἀπολλωνοπ<ex cert="high">ολίτου</ex></expan> <expan>π<ex cert="high">αρὰ</ex></expan> Γερμαν<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>ῦ </ab></div></div><div n="meta.19606" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.19606" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="0120" notBefore="0113" type="textDate">113 - 120</date></p></div><div n="meta.19606" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Tag: 8. (9.) Nov. Gehört zum Archiv des Strategen Apollonios. Datierung nach dem Rahmen des Archivs.</p></div><div n="meta.19606" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Brem.</title><biblScope type="numbers">21</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">19606</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0083</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">21</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0083;;21" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.19606" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">Welt aus Schnipseln, S. 76, Abbildung 38</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.19606" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="low" type="ancientFindspot">Hermopolis</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>